Filter:
    Filters are used to format the application data based on application requirements.
    We have two types of filters:
    1. Pre-defined filters
    2. Custom filters

  Pre-Defined filters: The filters given by the frameworks called as predefined filters.
  Custom filters: The filters developed by developer based on application requirements



1. uppercase

2. lowercase

3. currency

4. orderBy (+ --> assending - --> decending)

5. limitTo

6. filter

7. date



custom filters:
    - creating our own filter based on application requirement called as custom filter.


Syntax.

    app.filter("my_filter",my_filter);
    function my_filter(){
        return function(arg1,arg2,arg3,arg4,.....){
            //Code
        }
    }













